HEADWORD: Jnr.
<hw>Jnr.</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Abbreviation for <sig>Junior</sig>,
used after a name by a son who has the same first and last name as his
father; -- less commonly used than <altname>Jr.</altname></def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Junior, Jr.</syn>⟦br⟧
